{"tid":541633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣東省政協：廣東出口最佳產品「確確實實無私奉獻」　港人吃喝要感恩","createTime":"2018-01-26T15:53:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T10:28:35.000Z","uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":272,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"0e60ad5de503c9938d51dd7c7daaa31a8eba30a4","tid":541633,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T15:53:09.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/25204939/image1516884523260.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2F25204939%2Fimage1516884523260.png&h=3f671f6a&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n廣東省近日就粵港澳大灣區召開政協會議。有線中國組報道，廣東省政協委員周世明於會上建議，「香港、澳門的同胞更多要回到廣州這邊」，要明白廣東為香港「確確實實很無私的奉獻」，最好的東西多數都出口香港，「我們自己吃的是二流的、三流的產品」，香港人吃喝廣東的食物，就要有感恩的心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.post852.com/241099/%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E7%9C%81%E6%94%BF%E5%8D%94%EF%BC%9A%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%B3%E7%94%A2%E5%93%81%E3%80%8C%E7%A2%BA%E7%A2%BA%E5%AF%A6%E5%AF%A6%E7%84%A1%E7%A7%81%E5%A5%89/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F241099%2F%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E6%259D%25B1%25E7%259C%2581%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258D%2594%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E6%259D%25B1%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%258F%25A3%25E6%259C%2580%25E4%25BD%25B3%25E7%2594%25A2%25E5%2593%2581%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25A7%2581%25E5%25A5%2589%2F&d=M8Am0SjpHTpxvw2eHDqkxgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=62210a58\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.post852.com/241099/%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E7%9C%81%E6%94%BF%E5%8D%94%EF%BC%9A%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%B3%E7%94%A2%E5%93%81%E3%80%8C%E7%A2%BA%E7%A2%BA%E5%AF%A6%E5%AF%A6%E7%84%A1%E7%A7%81%E5%A5%89/</a>"},{"pid":"0e47c084ccca0fa0133744e2fbf16741ddad2584","tid":541633,"uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T15:55:17.000Z","msg":"【廣東政協委員指廣東為香港無私奉獻】<br />\n【港人應用感恩的心對待廣東】<br />\n<br />\n正在召開的廣東政協會議，專門開了一個座談會，讓委員發表對粵港澳大灣區的看法。廣東省政協委員周世明表示，香港應該對廣東感恩：「你要懂得廣東為香港確確實實很無私的奉獻，把最好的東西，多數都出口香港，我們自己吃的是二流的、三流的產品。你想想喝了這個，吃了這個，就要用感恩的心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。」<br />\n<br />\n另一名委員王曉華就表示，支那和港澳之間要有更緊密合作，包括在司法方面：「香港回歸了有多少年了，粵港澳之間的經濟上差距在縮小，但是為甚麼香港現在還是出現港獨的言論，包括佔中這些問題，這都是我們應該思考的問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1621228241354989/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1621228241354989%2F&d=M8Am0SjpHTpxvw2eHDqkxgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=8a59e6a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1621228241354989/</a>"},{"pid":"2b2d86130eaa4f35382b3eb50d8891b4da605a59","tid":541633,"uid":103325,"like":190,"dislike":1,"score":189,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T15:55:49.000Z","msg":"無私奉獻？我地無俾錢買架？"},{"pid":"5efec912bc1b472e4359720b61c61ee1f1cf93cb","tid":541633,"uid":33422,"like":132,"dislike":1,"score":131,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T15:59:50.000Z","msg":"食你啲屎，飲你啲東江尿水，無俾錢你哋呀？<br />\n<br />\n仲未計班廢物水貨狗一喼喼咁運奶粉生活品俾你哋班支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4390f223b83fbbe8dd2f695b0d1be6663a1a21","tid":541633,"uid":59773,"like":92,"dislike":1,"score":91,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T16:01:31.000Z","msg":"日本將lexus, infiniti等高級日本車賣去外國，都係無私奉獻。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d3441cd9ed7823aeeeeb4cca342c14009c4caf","tid":541633,"uid":110019,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T16:03:06.000Z","msg":"香港大把進口野食，你出口d劣質野嚟有撚人買咩，on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj